lor: red;\">所以我地901一齊入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1PM</span></span> 到機場吖<br />\n<br />\n誓要討回公道、要政府正面回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q：可能你會問，機場出咗禁制令，點解仲要入機場？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA：<br />\n禁制令=藐視法庭最多判幾月內(黃之峰坐左)<br />\n<br />\n非法集結起步判幾月<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪起步判3年以上至6年(梁天琦坐緊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法集會嚴重過藐視法庭啊</span></span><br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n明白個遊戲點玩未？？<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜都咁多手足俾人拉咗，分分鐘坐幾年甚至十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你真係甘心佢地咁努力，然後我地白費曬佢地嘅心機？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有勇氣上街頭勇武<br />\n點解唔敢入機場？</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6dd380683412c2a0188a9de1cae832bb84a38a71","tid":1512754,"uid":42042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"唉 DNLM<br />\n放工遲咗就俾人拎晒了，你班hihi<br />\n留返啲俾我吖diu你地<br />\n<br />\nps 20190828 中環ATM"},{"pid":"311eccec3f2dadb16ebdc46a317b0decb11fc096","tid":1512754,"uid":42042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd380683412c2a0188a9de1cae832bb84a38a71","tid":1512754,"uid":42042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"唉 DNLM<br />\n放工遲咗就俾人拎晒了，你班hihi<br />\n留返啲俾我吖diu你地<br />\n<br />\nps 20190828 中環ATM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESpcFfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESpcFfS.jpg&h=aeec7cda&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}